description: The Fund aims to achieve a return on your investment, through a combination of capital growth and income on the Fund’s assets, which reflects the return of the J.P. Morgan ESG EMBI Global Diversified IG Index, the Fund’s benchmark index (Index). On 24th April 2024, the benchmark changed from JP Morgan EMBI Global Diversified IG Index to J.P. Morgan ESG EMBI Global Diversified IG Index. The change will be reflected in the benchmark data.
name: iShares JP Morgan Advanced EM Investment Grade Bond UCITS ETF
